sentences.sentence: The objective is to investigate the effects of tiletamine on NO and NOS by XFM.
sentences.translation: 目的是通过小型猪复方麻醉剂（XFM）来研究乙胺噻吩环己酮对一氧化氮（NO）的一氧化氮合酶（NOS）的作用。

sentences.sentence: Every one of our "yeses" and nos "has a cost."
sentences.translation: 我们每一次说“是”和“不是”都要付出一定的代价。

sentences.sentence: Two Ohio cities, Dayton and Cincinnati, made our list at Nos. 9 and 10.
sentences.translation: 俄亥俄州的两座城市，代顿和辛辛那提，分列排行榜第9和第10。
